body:
# Welcome

So, my name is Peter Luu and I'm a freelance frontend web developer. I like breaking things and fixing them (and hopefully, making them better). I like making things work, cutting out all the unnecessary stuff, and keeping things simple for my clients.

If you have any questions, shoot me an email at [peter@kinesisdigital.com.au](peter@kinesisdigital.com.au).
